description:
**A NOTE: Some of you heard this episode last week and others didn’t. It was flagged for being rated R and we here at SVU believe because of that it was bumped off streams soon after going live. Here it is again. Rated E for Explicit. G for Gee Thanks. N for Natch Beaut.**


This week, Caroline is in Hawaii and Jackie is in California and they’re talkin’ Poo-pouri, duffle bags, TSA Security Theater, and singing some songs! You love it!
